Jenilee Harrison https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jenilee_Harrison 0 Jenilee A. Harrison (born June 12, 1958) is an American actress possibly best known for her role as the replacement blonde roommate Cindy Snow on the hit sitcom Three's Company, between 1980 and 1982. She went on to play Jamie Ewing Barnes in Dallas from 1984 to 1986.
